<doc id="671569" wikidata="Q5568397" url="?curid=671569" title="Glendalough, Western Australia">
<text>Glendalough is a suburb of Perth, Western Australia in the local government area of the City of Stirling, about 6 kilometres from Perth&#x27;s central business district along the Mitchell Freeway. It was named after Glendalough in Ireland.

==Transport==

