* 15 Glendalough Station to Perth Busport – serves Harborne Street and Powis Street
* 85 Glendalough Station to Perth Busport – serves Harborne Street and Jon Sanders Drive
* 95 Glendalough Station to Subiaco Station – serves Harborne Street
* 407 Glendalough Station to Glendalough Station – Circular Route, serves Harborne Street and Parkland Road

