* Stone, John. &#x27;The Law, the Alphabet, and Samuel Johnson.&#x27; &quot;Anniversary Essays on Johnson&#x27;s Dictionary&quot;, ed. Jack Lynch and Anne McDermott(Cambridge UP, 2005).

