* Sandro Nielsen (2010): Specialised Translation Dictionaries for Learners. In: P. A. Fuertes-Olivera (ed.): &quot;Specialised Dictionaries for Learners&quot;, de Gruyter (Lexicographica. Series Maior 136), 69-82.
